::Feline::

She fell from the blasts as they hit her shoulder, body and left leg.
She lay on the ground for a moment. She leaked a little mech fluid 
from her shoulder.  She slowly got up on her knees and then stood up. 
She looked at him and let out a low growl. "I thought I said hit. 
Like as in punch, upper cut, and so on like that." She looked at the 
damage done to her body. She sighed, "But this wil work as well."  
She limped over to Skulletron.  She leaned over and kissed his cheek.
"Thanks handsome." She turned and took a few steps towards the ship.  
She turned and looked at him,"Don't worry, it all be purrrrrfect." 
She smiled at him and walked off.  She waved her tail at him in 
a 'Bye' motion as she limped her way to the ship.

--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "Jason Vorhees" <dcoburn@n...> wrote:
> ::Skulletron::
> 
>         Skulletron looks at Feline, puzzled, as she asks him to 
fire  on her a couple times.  That would be hard.  She was too 
beautiful for him to do that.  But then, his mind went towards the 
 mission and he Alliance.
> 
> 
"Alright then.  Anything to get this mission done!" 
Skulletron sighed as he grabbed his ray gun.
> 
He aimed it at her, finger on the trigger.  He clenched the 
gun tight, hands shaking.  Then he fired three blasts from his ray 
gun very quickly, shutting his eyes.
